            <description><![CDATA[吃肥肉会长胖吗？肥肉党们自觉收藏<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>肥肉全是脂肪，多吃一定会长胖！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[白眼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_landelini-609e5583df.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>越来越多的研究表明，脂肪摄入不仅不会导致体重增加，反而可能帮助我们减掉几磅！研究人员将低脂，高碳水化合物饮食，与高脂，低碳水化合物饮食的人进行了比较，发现变胖的罪魁祸首不是脂肪，而是添加糖和精制碳水化合物。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（健康界）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hitt7pmrytg20hq06g0tn.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
